data.title: TODAY IS THE BIRHDAY OF VAZGEN SARGSYAN: COMMEMORATE EVENT AT THE DEPARTMENT OF MANAGEMENT
data.meta_description: TODAY IS THE BIRHDAY  OF  VAZGEN SARGSYAN: COMMEMORATE  EVENT AT  THE  DEPARTMENT OF MANAGEMENT
data.text:
Today is the birthday of national, state and political figure Vazgen Sargsyan. The students hold on a lectur devoted to Vazgen Sargsyanâ€™s memory by the initiative of the Student Council of Department of Management.

The 1st course students of the Department of Management Ani Karapetyan, Mary Hayrapetyan, Lianna Sardaryan presented the biography of the hero and a documentary film.

At the end of the event The Vice Dean of the Department of Management Mary Badalyan thanked the students for organizing nice event.
